A FIRST LOOK AT PERTURBATION THEORY by James G. Simmonds, James E. Mann Jr.
A Guided Tour of Mathematical Physics / Roel Snieder http://samizdat.mines.edu/snieder/



參考書目 References
	    Mathematical models [electronic resource] : mechanical vibrations, population dynamics, and traffic flow : an introduction to applied mathematics / Richard Haberman. (參考圖書館電子書)    

備註 Remarks

目前課程規劃為：前半段主要依循 street-fighting-mathematics；第二部分是微擾法簡介； 最後則是傅立葉變換的簡介與應用
授課內容可能會依照修課學生背景調整，有任何建議歡迎於第一次上課提出
評分方式可能會調整






基本素養 Basic Literacy
        無    

核心能力 Competence
■ 掌握連續與逼進的能力
 Ability to handle continuity phenomena and approximations.
■ 處理數字及符號運算的能力
 Ability to operate with symbols and digits.
□ 透視形像與空間的能力
 Ability to visualize space, shape, and images.
■ 利用計算機處理數學的能力
 Ability of using computer to do mathematics.
□ 應用隨機理論的能力
 Ability to apply stochastic mathematics.
□ 處理大量數據的能力
 Ability to handle large amount of data.
■ 處理離散型數學的能力
 Ability to do mathematics relating to discrete models.
□ 獨立研究的能力
 Ability to do independent studies of mathematics.
■ 使用計算機的能力
 Abilities to use computer as a tool.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       本課程將介紹在不同的應用數學領域中所需要的基本方法。如尺度分析、因次分析、富氏分析、最佳化方法、微擾法、最速陡降法、牛頓法、共軛梯度法等等。本課程將帶領學生學習從應用層面切入去瞭解問題並採取適當的解決方案。Basic methods in applied mathematics are introduced, for example, scale analysis, dimensional analysis, Fourier analysis, perturbation method, steepest descent method, Newton method, conjugate gradient method, etc.. Students will learn how to solve problem in the applied mathematical point of view and take a suitable and reasonable solution.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
使用數學技巧在沒有複雜或精密的計算下估算出可能的答案使用微擾法將非線性問題簡化應用傅立葉變換 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction2Dimensions3Easy cases4Lumping5Pictorial proofs6Taking out the big part7Analogy8Review9Introduction of Perturbation Theory10Roots of Polynomials11Roots of Polynomials(Cont'd)12Singular Perturbations in Ordinary Differential Equations13Singular Perturbations in Ordinary Differential Equations(Cont'd)14Periodic Solutions15Fourier analysis16Fourier analysis (Cont'd)17Fourier analysis (Cont'd)18Topic 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


